nodes.text: Enouck was a group of 3 Lambda-class T-4a shuttles used by the Rebel Alliance. The shuttles were present at a depot attacked by an Imperial corvette Control that launched 3 TIE Bombers. The shuttles along with shuttle group Xarxis attempted to fight back by attacking the bombers but they were destroyed in the battle.
